Class LWJGLTimer

java.lang.Object
  com.golden.gamedev.engine.lwjgl.LWJGLTimer
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.golden.gamedev.engine.BaseTimer
public class LWJGLTimer
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.golden.gamedev.engine.BaseTimer

Timer engine used in LWJGL graphics environment,
LWJGL is available to download at http://lwjgl.org/.

Make sure the downloaded library is included into your game classpath before using this timer engine.

Note: GTGE is not associated in any way with LWJGL, this class is only interfacing LWJGL to be used in GTGE.
This class is created and has been tested to be working properly using LWJGL v0.95.
